'''CXCL10'''（{{lang-en|C-X-C motif chemokine 10}}）是一小分子的[[细胞因子|细胞因子]]属于CXC[[趋化因子|趋化因子]]家族<ref>Liu L, Callahan MK, Huang D, Ransohoff RM. Chemokine receptor CXCR3: an unexpected enigma. Curr Top Dev Biol. 2005;68:149-81.</ref>，又被称作“干扰素伽玛诱导的10千道尔顿蛋白”（10 kDa interferon-gamma-induced protein，IP-10）<ref>Kaplan G, Luster AD, Hancock G, Cohn ZA. The expression of a gamma interferon-induced protein (IP-10) in delayed immune responses in human skin. J Exp Med. 1987 Oct 1;166(4):1098-108.</ref> 。[[干扰素伽玛|干扰素伽玛]]可以在多种细胞（如[[巨噬细胞|巨噬细胞]]<ref name=nor>Narumi S, Hamilton TA. Inducible expression of murine IP-10 mRNA varies with the state of macrophage inflammatory activity. J Immunol. 1991 May 1;146(9):3038-44.</ref> ，[[单核细胞|单核细胞]]<ref name=nor>Narumi S, Hamilton TA. Inducible expression of murine IP-10 mRNA varies with the state of macrophage inflammatory activity. J Immunol. 1991 May 1;146(9):3038-44.</ref> ，[[内皮细胞|内皮细胞]]<ref name=ang>Angiolillo AL, Sgadari C, Taub DD, Liao F, Farber JM, Maheshwari S, Kleinman HK, Reaman GH, Tosato G. Human interferon-inducible protein 10 is a potent inhibitor of angiogenesis in vivo. J Exp Med. 1995 Jul 1;182(1):155-62.</ref>和[[成纤维细胞|成纤维细胞]]）中诱导CXCL10的表达。CXCL10的功能包括对[[T细胞|T细胞]]和单核细胞的细胞趋化作用<ref name=chemo>Loetscher M, Gerber B, Loetscher P, Jones SA, Piali L, Clark-Lewis I, Baggiolini M, Moser B. Chemokine receptor specific for IP10 and mig: structure, function, and expression in activated T-lymphocytes. J Exp Med. 1996 Sep 1;184(3):963-9.</ref><ref name=fun>Weng Y, Siciliano SJ, Waldburger KE, Sirotina-Meisher A, Staruch MJ, Daugherty BL, Gould SL, Springer MS, DeMartino JA. Binding and functional properties of recombinant and endogenous CXCR3 chemokine receptors. J Biol Chem. 1998 Jul 17;273(29):18288-91.</ref>，促进T细胞黏附于内皮细胞<ref name=ang>Angiolillo AL, Sgadari C, Taub DD, Liao F, Farber JM, Maheshwari S, Kleinman HK, Reaman GH, Tosato G. Human interferon-inducible protein 10 is a potent inhibitor of angiogenesis in vivo. J Exp Med. 1995 Jul 1;182(1):155-62.</ref>，抗[[肿瘤|肿瘤]]<ref>Luster AD, Leder P. IP-10, a -C-X-C- chemokine, elicits a potent thymus-dependent antitumor response in vivo. J Exp Med. 1993 Sep 1;178(3):1057-65</ref>，及[[血管新生|血管新生]]<ref name=ang>Angiolillo AL, Sgadari C, Taub DD, Liao F, Farber JM, Maheshwari S, Kleinman HK, Reaman GH, Tosato G. Human interferon-inducible protein 10 is a potent inhibitor of angiogenesis in vivo. J Exp Med. 1995 Jul 1;182(1):155-62.</ref>。人类的CXCL10基因与[[CXCL9|CXCL9]]，[[CXCL11|CXCL11]]的基因相邻聚集在第四染色体上。CXCL10, CXCL9和CXCL11结合[[趋化因子受体|趋化因子受体]][[CXCR3|CXCR3]]而起其细胞趋化作用<ref name=chemo>Loetscher M, Gerber B, Loetscher P, Jones SA, Piali L, Clark-Lewis I, Baggiolini M, Moser B. Chemokine receptor specific for IP10 and mig: structure, function, and expression in activated T-lymphocytes. J Exp Med. 1996 Sep 1;184(3):963-9.</ref><ref name=fun>Weng Y, Siciliano SJ, Waldburger KE, Sirotina-Meisher A, Staruch MJ, Daugherty BL, Gould SL, Springer MS, DeMartino JA. Binding and functional properties of recombinant and endogenous CXCR3 chemokine receptors. J Biol Chem. 1998 Jul 17;273(29):18288-91.</ref> 。

